flowchart TD
    Start([Register an Account]) --> Profile[Complete Profile]
    Profile --> CreateShop[Create a Shop]
    CreateShop --> Pending[Shop Status: Pending Approval]

    Pending --> AdminDecision{Admin Reviews Shop}
    AdminDecision -- Approved --> Live[Shop is Live & Visible to Buyers]
    AdminDecision -- Suspended --> Fix[Address Issues]
    Fix --> CreateShop

    Live --> AddProducts[Add Products\nName · Price · Stock · Images]
    AddProducts --> Wait[Wait for Customer Orders]

    Wait --> NewOrder[New Order Arrives!]
    NewOrder --> Confirm[Confirm Order]
    Confirm --> Prepare[Prepare the Package]
    Prepare --> Ship[Mark as Shipped]
    Ship --> Delivery[Buyer Receives Package\nand Confirms Receipt]

    Delivery --> Revenue[Order Revenue Recorded\npayout_id = null]
    Revenue --> Wait

    Revenue --> PayoutCycle[Admin Calculates Payout\nGross minus Commission]
    PayoutCycle --> NetPaid[Receive Net Payment\nTransaction Ref Logged]

    NewOrder --> Messages[Customer Sends a Message]
    Messages --> Reply[Reply via Seller Messages Inbox]
    Reply --> Wait

    NewOrder --> Dispute{Customer Files Dispute?}
    Dispute -- Yes --> Escalated[Support Ticket Created\nAdmin Mediates]
    Dispute -- No --> Wait
    Escalated --> AdminResolves([Admin Resolves the Issue])

    Live --> ShopSettings[Update Shop Info\nLogo · Banner · Contact]
    ShopSettings --> Live

    Live --> ManageProducts[Edit or Deactivate Products]
    ManageProducts --> Live
